This wonderful Pisco recipe is one of many great recipes from the @beautifulbooze book.

Angry Inca Orchid 

45 ml Pisco quebranta
60 ml ruby red grapefruit juice
15 ml lavender syrup
Aquafaba
A pinch of salt 

Shake with plenty of ice, take out the ice and shake dry. Poor in a chilled coupe and enjoy! 

Proost! Salute! Cheers!
